rgetTime=13&hitYear=2013&termGbn=week |title=Just Go |date=23 March 2013 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''Just Go (Goodbye's The New Hello)''\n|\n* Released: 8 February, 2013\n* Label: DR Music, Yedang Company\n* Format: [[Compact disc|CD]], Digital download.\n{{hidden|Track list|\n# \"Just Go\" \n# \"Secret Party\"\n# \"Killer\"\n# \"Style\"\n# \"Dr. Feel Good\"\n# \"Masquerade\"\n# \"Pop Pop Pop\"\n# \"Goodbye\"\n# \"Just Go (English Ver.)\"\n# \"Dr. Feel Good (English Ver.)\"\n# \"Masquerade (English Ver.)\"\n}}\n| \u2014\n| {{N/A}}\n|-\n|}\n\n===Extended plays===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:15em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:20em;\"| Album details\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak chart positions\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\" |[[Gaon Albums Chart|KOR]]<br><ref name=\"GaonAlbum\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Teddy Riley, the First Expansion In Asia''\n|\n* Released: 6 April 2011\n* Label: DR Music, Yedang Company\n* Format: [[Music download|Digital download]]\n{{hidden|Track list|\n# \"Dr. Feel Good\"\n# \"Masquerade\"\n# \"Dr Feel Good\" <small>(English version)</small>\n# \"Masquerade\" <small>(English version)</small>\n# \"Dr. Feel Good\" <small>(Instrumental)</small>\n# \"Masquerade\" <small>(Instrumental)</small>\n}}\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Time to Rock da Show]]''\n|\n* Released: 17 November 2011\n* Label: DR Music, Yedang Company\n* Format: [[Music download|Digital download]]\n{{hidden|Track list|\n# \"Time to Rock da Show\" <small>(Introduction)</small>\n# \"Pop Pop Pop\" \n# \"Goodbye\"\n# \"Pop Pop Pop\" <small>(Instrumental)</small>\n}}\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''[[Demonstrate (EP)|Demonstrate]]''\n|\n* Released: 5 November 2015\n* Label: DR Music, Danal Entertainment\n* Format: [[Compact disc|CD]], [[Music download|digital download]]\n{{hidden|Track list|\n# \"Demonstrate\"\n# \"Hello\"\n# \"Get Out\"\n# \